                <title>Layer.activeAtTime()</title>
                <paragraph><literal>app.project.item(index).layer(index).activeAtTime(time)</literal></paragraph>
                <paragraph><strong>Description</strong></paragraph>
                <paragraph>Returns true if this layer will be active at the specified time.</paragraph>
                <paragraph>To return <literal>true</literal>, the layer must be enabled, no other layer may be soloing unless this layer is soloed too, and the time must be between the <literal>inPoint</literal> and <literal>outPoint</literal> values of this layer.</paragraph>
